<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-17 17:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6772 &Cx1f; kan-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FUGITIVE-TRIAL-KAN &LR;      01-17 0886
