   NATION
</P>
<P>
   GLOBAL-CITIZENS _ ATLANTA _ Global Citizens Circle gathering in
Atlanta brings together John Hume of Northern Ireland, Desmond
Tutu, Coretta Scott King and Andrew Young to discuss ``How do we
achieve true reconciliation?'' (Walston, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 15-20. WITH PHOTO. ETA: 7:30 p.m. EDT
</P>
<P>
   FALCONS-FANS _ ATLANTA _ All-purpose fans-back-home piece with
quotes from folks watching Falcons-Vikings game, the presumed rush
on Superbowl travel packages should the Dirty Birds win and, for
5-star, the return of the victors or vanquished at Hartsfield (est.
arrival time 9 p.m.). (Staff, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH
PHOTO.
