<P>
   TEXAS-INAUG-LOGISTICS _ AUSTIN _ Nitty gritty logistics of the
inauguration. You've heard about the fun and the parties, now what
about security arrangements? Traffic tie ups? Parking? Police
patrols? The Secret Service? The anti-sniper unit? What to do if
you have state or other business downtown that day. Etc. (Osborn,
