   2-column hed.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BOTTOM: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SANFRAN-SPCA (San Francisco) _ San Francisco's SPCA not only has
a no-kill policy for the pets left with it, but plush
accommodations for them, too. Now it has $200 million to take
no-kill national. By Evelyn Nieves. (With photos.)
</P>
